2f2c772b-bed1-47f2-be88-9be1cff82871.do_description: To make the output, you have to... copy the input grid. Find any shapes outside of the border which are exactly the same shape and orientation as the shape inside of the grey border. Turn that shape grey. Do not change the colored shape inside the grey border or any shapes outside of the grey border which do not have the same orientation and shape as the one inside the border.
2f2c772b-bed1-47f2-be88-9be1cff82871.grid_description: The output grid size... is the same as the input size.
2f2c772b-bed1-47f2-be88-9be1cff82871.see_description: In the input, you should see... a number of colored shapes including one with a grey border around it.

64130b9c-5cae-44d9-8dfe-b6a4a576d187.do_description: To make the output, you have to...find the shape closest to a corner that isn't the top left corner. Color that shape the same color as the box in the top left.
64130b9c-5cae-44d9-8dfe-b6a4a576d187.grid_description: The output grid size...should be the same as the input.
64130b9c-5cae-44d9-8dfe-b6a4a576d187.see_description: In the input, you should see...a bunch of shapes of various shapes and a shape in the top left enclosed in a box.

6ef9ad5e-a62f-4b99-b59f-be395620ddba.do_description: To make the output, you have to...change object on the rightmost grid to gray
6ef9ad5e-a62f-4b99-b59f-be395620ddba.see_description: In the input, you should see...different objects of different colors

bcc573fe-0f2c-4898-b1fc-eb01dd17f76e.do_description: To make the output, you have to...color one gray on the right a color that is not already in use
bcc573fe-0f2c-4898-b1fc-eb01dd17f76e.grid_description: The output grid size...should remain the same.
bcc573fe-0f2c-4898-b1fc-eb01dd17f76e.see_description: In the input, you should see...a 10x10 grid

e8f85f91-418d-40fa-9387-522ffe33d16c.do_description: To make the output, you have to...from the right column to left get the first pattern, if there is no same color pattern then change its color to grey, otherwise pass it and keep check on form right to left column.
e8f85f91-418d-40fa-9387-522ffe33d16c.grid_description: The output grid size...the same size
e8f85f91-418d-40fa-9387-522ffe33d16c.see_description: In the input, you should see...many color patterns, different size and different shape
